& Principle T his is an eternal and fundamentalprinciple, inherent in all
things, in every system of philosophy, in everyreligion and in every
science. There isno getting away from the law of love. Itis feeling that
imparts vitality tothought. Feeling is desire, and desire islove. Thought
impregnated with lovebecomes invincible.
